Copyright 2026 Andreas Drozd

This product includes software developed by:

  - Andreas Drozd (originally authored thesis artifacts)

This artifact accompanies the bachelor thesis
"Sidecar vs. Ambient: Telemetry Reliability and Automated Canary Remediation
in a GitOps-Managed Kubernetes Environment", Hochschule Campus Wien, Computer Science
and Digital Communications, SS 2026.

Original works in this repository (Apache-2.0):
  - Shell scripts under scripts/
  - Python analysis under analysis/
  - All 7 Grafana dashboards under manifests/monitoring/dashboards/
    (originally authored, no gnetId/__inputs from grafana.com)
  - PrometheusRule, Argo WorkflowTemplate, EventSource, Sensor manifests
    under manifests/automation/ and manifests/monitoring/
  - ArgoCD AppProject and Application manifests under manifests/argocd/
    and manifests/experiments/
  - All documentation under docs/

