============================================================================
Pyroscope and Tempo dashboard inspiration
============================================================================
The dashboards manifests/monitoring/dashboards/ba2-profiles-dashboard-cm.yaml
and ba2-traces-dashboard-cm.yaml were authored from scratch for this thesis
and use queries documented in upstream Pyroscope and Tempo documentation.
No Grafana JSON was imported from community.grafana.com; no gnetId or
__inputs fields are present.

  Pyroscope:  https://github.com/grafana/pyroscope
              License: AGPL-3.0 (the dashboard source code is original; only
              the metric and profile names referenced are from upstream)
  Tempo:      https://github.com/grafana/tempo
              License: AGPL-3.0 (same caveat)
